<section class="page-margin contained">
    <h2 id="user-research">User research</h2>
    <p>To enhance our knowledge and better understand who would be using this software, my research colleague and I attended a day-long HDD training seminar at a local community college. An extremely eye opening opportunity, we talked to a variety of vendors and introduced ourselves to a couple drill crews who let us ask them questions and get feedback on our early ideas for the auto-correct feature.</p>
</section>

