<section class="page-margin contained">
    <h2>Testing outdoors</h2>
    <p>Once I got the look and feel to a branded state, I brought the rugged PC home to examine the contrast and readability of the interface on a bright, sunny day. I managed to test the display using it’s default factory settings, as well as at 100-percent brightness. These tests led me to increasing in the minimum font size and darkening of some colors that had already met WCAG standards but were still diffult to see in full sunlight. </p>
</section>

